_aFiles._sDescription: contains the .bsp and .nav with a README incase you dont know what to do

_sText:
cp_zombieapartment was a map i made a while ago, i was gonna publish it in a pack with other maps made by my friend pbow but he kinda gave up on that i guess so i throught i would publish it by itself now for you all to enjoy,

its a simple but atleast i'd like to believe decent map to play with friends or bots

also if you want to know why its called zombie apartment its because i originally made the map to play with bots that use knifes only but then i ended up turning it into a normal map and just never changed its name.
